1. Install Apache and Mysql  
2. Create database
    mysql> 
    create database db;
    use  db;
    CREATE TABLE `users`( `id` INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`email` VARCHAR(45) NULL,`password` VARCHAR(45) NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`));
    insert into users (email,password) values ('admin@admin.com','abc123');
    insert into users (email,password) values ('admin@admin.com',md5('abc123'));
3. Copy login.php and welcome.php to www directory
4. Browse localhost/login.php and test it

